<T>__{dissolve to:}
<L>__{exterior ridgemont hallway morning}
<A>__{the bell has just rung, and mike damone comes out of youth and law class. he has an absorbed, driven look on his face. he walks past the rows of lockers, and doesn't even notice as he passes stacy hamilton standing by her locker. she smiles, grabs his arm affectionately.}
<C>__{stacy}
<D>__{hi mike!}
<A>__{damone turns to see her, is thoroughly unimpressed.}
<C>__{damone}
<D>__{oh. hi.}
<C>__{stacy}
<D>__{i didn't see you this morning.}
<C>__{damone}
<D>__{look, i'm kind of in a hurry.}
<C>__{stacy}
<D>__{i'm in a hurry too. i just thought i could say hi to you.}
<C>__{damone}
<D>__{hello.}
<A>__{he pulls away, leaving a bewildered stacy standing by her locker. she grabs some books and hurries in the other direction.}
